if he fought Sugar Ray,

17
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:50,763
he would say that the thing
ain't the ring, it's the play.

18
00:03:50,867 --> 00:03:54,268
So, give me a stage where
this bull here can rage,

19
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:57,339
and though I can fight,
I'd much rather recite.

20
00:03:58,474 --> 00:03:59,998
That's entertainment.

21
00:04:05,615 --> 00:04:07,048
That's entertainment.

22
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:08,777
Jake La Motta
and Jimmy Reeves

23
00:04:08,885 --> 00:04:10,352
in the Cleveland Arena.

24
00:04:10,453 --> 00:04:13,479
La Motta is undefeated,
but he's well behind on points.

25
00:04:13,589 --> 00:04:16,683
