924
01:03:16,168 --> 01:03:16,963
But you don't raise your hands,

925
01:03:17,134 --> 01:03:20,399
you don't create a scene
like that in a place like that.

926
01:03:20,504 --> 01:03:23,234
Now, we've heard
everybody's point of view here,

927
01:03:23,340 --> 01:03:25,501
and we're gonna forget about it.

928
01:03:25,609 --> 01:03:29,067
I shouldn't forget about it,
but we're gonna forget about it.

929
01:03:29,713 --> 01:03:30,839
Right?

930
01:03:30,948 --> 01:03:33,007
What I want you to do now,
you two guys,

931
01:03:33,117 --> 01:03:36,211
I want you to shake hands,
forget this whole thing,

932
01:03:36,320 --> 01:03:37,844
and no grudges.

933
01:03:37,955 --> 01:03:40,753
That's the most important thing--
no grudges.

934
01:03:41,725 --> 01:03:43,522
Now, come on, shake hands.

935
01:03:48,232 --> 01:03:50,700
It's all right with me
if it's all right with you.

936
01:03:50,801 --> 01:03:51,927
All right?

937
01:03:52,836 --> 01:03:54,963
I only wish this thing
never happened.

938
01:03:55,072 --> 01:03:56,903
We all wish it never happened.

939
01:03:57,007 --> 01:04:00,135
Right?
You'll get over it.

940
01:04:00,244 --> 01:04:03,372
Salvy, let me talk
with him alone a minute.

941
01:04:03,480 --> 01:04:04,606
Yeah, all right.

942
01:04:06,783 --> 01:04:09,081
I'll see you Monday,
Tuesday or somethin', all right?

943
01:04:09,186 --> 01:04:11,211
I'm sorry,
I forgot all about it.

944
01:04:11,755 --> 01:04:14,553
What are you, fucking nuts?
You're killin' me.

945
01:04:19,463 --> 01:04:22,330
Aside from everything else,
is the family all right?

946
01:04:22,432 --> 01:04:25,196
Yeah, they're fine.
Everybody's fine.

947
01:04:28,939 --> 01:04:30,998
What is it with you?
You can't talk?

948
01:04:31,108 --> 01:04:32,632
- I'm talkin', what do you mean?
- I know.

949
01:04:32,743 --> 01:04:36,008
Why have you got this funny attitude?
I can't figure you out.

950
01:04:36,547 --> 01:04:40,176
What is it with all the quick answers?
"Yeah, they're all right. Yeah."

951
01:04:41,385 --> 01:04:43,444
You wanna get outta here
fast or something?

952
01:04:43,554 --> 01:04:44,919
No, it's nothin' like that.

953
01:04:45,022 --> 01:04:47,923
It's just all the aggravation
and everything and...

954
01:04:48,492 --> 01:04:49,959
all the fights and all.

955
01:04:51,728 --> 01:04:54,162
Listen to me.
Now, Jake...

956
01:04:55,098 --> 01:04:57,692
the guy's become
an embarrassment.

957
01:04:58,402 --> 01:05:01,530
He's embarrassin' me
with certain people,

958
01:05:01,638 --> 01:05:03,902
and I'm lookin' very bad.

959
01:05:04,575 --> 01:05:07,874
I can't deliver a kid from
my own goddamn neighborhood.

960
01:05:08,412 --> 01:05:09,470
What is it with him?

961
01:05:09,580 --> 01:05:12,549
Why does he have to make it
so hard on himself?

962
01:05:12,649 --> 01:05:15,277
He comes to me,
I make it easier for him.

963
01:05:18,255 --> 01:05:20,382
The man's got a head of rock.

964
01:05:25,028 --> 01:05:27,826
You know, it's hard
to explain, Tommy, he's...

965
01:05:28,532 --> 01:05:29,829
Jack respects you.

966
01:05:29,933 --> 01:05:32,401
I mean, he don't even
say hello to anybody.

967
01:05:32,502 --> 01:05:34,800
You he talks to, he likes you.

968
01:05:36,306 --> 01:05:38,900
It's just that when he gets
somethin' on his mind,

969
01:05:39,009 --> 01:05:42,001
he's got a hard head,
he likes to do things his own way.

970
01:05:42,112 --> 01:05:44,478
Jesus Christ could
come off the cross sometimes,

971
01:05:44,581 --> 01:05:47,015
he don't give a fuck,
he's gonna do what he wants to do,

972
01:05:47,117 --> 01:05:50,143
he wants to make it on his own.
He thinks he can make it on his own.

973
01:05:50,254 --> 01:05:51,551
Make it on his own.

974
01:05:51,655 --> 01:05:56,718
He thinks he's gonna walk in there
and become champion on his own?

975
01:05:57,461 --> 01:06:00,294
- He's crazy. You know he's nuts.
- Yeah, he's crazy.

976
01:06:00,397 --> 01:06:03,798
And he's got no respect for nobody,
he doesn't listen to nobody.

977
01:06:03,900 --> 01:06:05,197
That's not crazy.

978
01:06:05,302 --> 01:06:08,703
- He respects you, though.
- He doesn't respect anybody.

979
01:06:08,805 --> 01:06:10,932
Now, you do this for me,
you understand?

980
01:06:11,041 --> 01:06:16,240
You tell him I don't care
how colorful he is, how great he is.

981
01:06:16,346 --> 01:06:17,973
He could beat all
the Sugar Ray Robinsons

982
01:06:18,081 --> 01:06:20,106
and the Tony Janiros in the world.

983
01:06:20,217 --> 01:06:23,778
But he ain't gonna get a shot
at that title, not without us, he ain't.

984
01:06:24,621 --> 01:06:26,714
Now, you're a smart kid.

985
01:06:27,090 --> 01:06:29,217
You go to him, you tell him...

986
01:06:34,364 --> 01:06:35,661
Son of a bitch.

987
01:06:36,700 --> 01:06:38,327
Twenty dollar shoe here.

988
01:06:45,542 --> 01:06:47,510
Aren't you gonna
ask me what happened?

989
01:06:51,715 --> 01:06:52,841
What's the matter?

990
01:06:55,552 --> 01:06:58,180
- What's wrong?
- I remember when I met her here.

991
01:06:59,222 --> 01:07:01,349
- Who?
- Vickie.

992
01:07:04,394 --> 01:07:07,363
Why, what's the matter?
What'd she do now?

993
01:07:10,701 --> 01:07:13,636
I know she's doin' somethin',
I just wanna catch her once.

994
01:07:13,737 --> 01:07:14,863
Just once.

995
01:07:18,475 --> 01:07:21,444
Hey, Jack.
Wanna do yourself a favor?

996
01:07:21,978 --> 01:07:24,208
Bust her fuckin' hole,
throw her out.

997
01:07:24,748 --> 01:07:27,308
Either that, or live with her
and let her ruin your life,

998
01:07:27,417 --> 01:07:29,214
'cause that's what's happenin'.

999
01:07:32,022 --> 01:07:34,991
How much could you take?
How much shit could you take?

1000
01:07:44,868 --> 01:07:46,426
So, what'd that guy say?

1001
01:07:47,371 --> 01:07:49,999
He gave me the old
"good news, bad news" routine.

1002
01:07:50,540 --> 01:07:51,598
The good news is

1003
01:07:51,708 --> 01:07:53,835
you're gonna get
the shot at the title.

1004
01:07:53,944 --> 01:07:58,176
The bad news is they want you
to do the old flip-flop for them.

1005
01:07:59,282 --> 01:08:01,273
- So, what else is new?
- What'd you expect?

1006
01:08:01,385 --> 01:08:02,818
You didn't know that was comin'?

1007
01:08:03,887 --> 01:08:05,548
You win some,
you lose some.

1008
01:08:05,655 --> 01:08:07,122
This one, we're losin'.

1009
01:08:09,459 --> 01:08:10,585
Billy Fox.

1010
01:08:11,128 --> 01:08:14,928
173 and 3/4 pounds.

1011
01:08:17,501 --> 01:08:21,801
- Jake La Motta. 167...
- I guess you've heard by now

1012
01:08:21,905 --> 01:08:25,170
a lot of the stuff that's
goin' around, a lot of rumors.

1013
01:08:25,709 --> 01:08:29,008
Matter of fact, a short time ago
you were a big favorite,

1014
01:08:29,112 --> 01:08:31,478
and all of a sudden,
you're a 12-5 underdog,

1015
01:08:31,581 --> 01:08:33,572
and people are talkin',
it's as simple as that.

1016
01:08:33,683 --> 01:08:36,481
- That's funny, I never heard anything.
- It's out there, though,

1017
01:08:36,586 --> 01:08:37,644
and It's not good.

1018
01:08:37,754 --> 01:08:39,722
As a matter of fact,
the bets are off on this one.

1019
01:08:39,823 --> 01:08:41,654
Nothin' goin' in this one.

1020
01:08:41,758 --> 01:08:45,592
Matter of fact, smart money is sayin'
that you're getting ready to hit the tank.

1021
01:08:45,695 --> 01:08:47,890
- That's bullshit.
- Yeah, that's bullshit.

1022
01:08:48,865 --> 01:08:50,162
You got any money
you wanna bet?

1023
01:08:50,267 --> 01:08:51,825
- Come on.
- I'll take the action, go ahead.

1024
01:08:51,935 --> 01:08:54,733
You bet it on Fox,
'cause I'm gonna win.

1025
01:08:54,838 --> 01:08:57,170
There's no way I'm goin' down.
I don't go down for nobody.

1026
01:08:57,274 --> 01:08:59,071
- That's what I wanted to hear.
- I want you to know that.

1027
01:08:59,176 --> 01:09:00,643
- All right.
- All right, Colonel.

1028
01:09:00,744 --> 01:09:02,234
Okay, that's it.

1029
01:09:02,345 --> 01:09:03,676
You came down here just
for that nonsense?

1030
01:09:03,780 --> 01:09:05,475
- That was it?
- That was it.

1031
01:09:15,926 --> 01:09:17,518
Good evening,
ladies and gentlemen.

1032
01:09:17,627 --> 01:09:20,528
Welcome to
the Madison Square Garden

1033
01:09:20,630 --> 01:09:22,723
feature attraction.

1034
01:09:22,833 --> 01:09:27,395
- In this corner, weighing 175 pounds...
- Commissioner, how about a picture?

1035
01:09:27,504 --> 01:09:29,301
Fellas, can we get
a picture over here?

1036
01:09:29,406 --> 01:09:33,206
...the undefeated Billy Fox.

1037
01:09:37,013 --> 01:09:39,072
Hi, Steve. Your brother
got out of the hospital?

1038
01:09:39,182 --> 01:09:42,174
- They think it's all right.
- Did he get out? Good.

1039
01:09:43,987 --> 01:09:46,455
- Charlie, let me sit over there.
- Yeah, sure.

1040
01:09:47,858 --> 01:09:50,554
Tommy, what's the matter?
Everything's all right?

1041
01:09:50,660 --> 01:09:52,093
It's all right, yeah.

1042
01:09:52,195 --> 01:09:53,856
Touch gloves now,
come out boxing.

1043
01:09:53,964 --> 01:09:55,761
Five seconds, Alex.

1044
01:10:08,378 --> 01:10:11,074
Come on, stand--
come on, stand up!

1045
01:10:11,181 --> 01:10:13,877
What the fuck you doin'?
Hit me, ya fuckin' bum, come on.

1046
01:10:14,551 --> 01:10:15,677
Come on.

1047
01:10:16,319 --> 01:10:19,720
What are you doin', Jake?!
Come on, box him!

1048
01:10:29,566 --> 01:10:31,363
What the fuck's
the matter with you?

1049
01:10:31,902 --> 01:10:33,961
What do you think
you're doin' out there?!

1050
01:10:34,070 --> 01:10:35,367
- Huh?
- Little slow, that's all.

1051
01:10:35,472 --> 01:10:38,032
- What are you doin' out there?
- Take it easy, he'll be all right.

1052
01:10:38,141 --> 01:10:41,304
He's a little slow. He'll make it up,
what are ya worried about?

1053
01:10:41,411 --> 01:10:44,972
Goddamn it. Come on,
pick it up a little, Jake, I'm sorry.

1054
01:10:45,081 --> 01:10:47,311
Come on, Jake,
I got some money on ya!

1055
01:10:47,918 --> 01:10:50,079
- Tank job!
- Hit him back, ya bum!

1056
01:10:50,186 --> 01:10:51,483
- Come on.
- Hit him back!

1057
01:10:52,422 --> 01:10:55,357
You fuckin' bum!
You're takin' a dive in the fourth?

1058
01:10:55,892 --> 01:10:57,985
Pocket your dirty money!

1059
01:11:00,530 --> 01:11:03,158
Aw, you phony bastard!
That's a fix!

1060
01:11:03,266 --> 01:11:04,824
We're stoppin' the fight!

1061
01:11:05,402 --> 01:11:08,701
What the fuck are you waitin' for
to stop the fight, ya jerk?!

1062
01:11:09,272 --> 01:11:10,330
And you standin' there.

1063
01:11:10,440 --> 01:11:13,432
- Fuckin' go down, will ya?
- The referee stops this bout

1064
01:11:13,543 --> 01:11:18,242
at 2:23 of the fourth round.

1065
01:11:18,348 --> 01:11:21,749
The winner
by technical knockout,

1066
01:11:21,851 --> 01:11:24,012
and still undefeated,

1067
01:11:24,120 --> 01:11:27,112
Billy Fox!

1068
01:11:28,892 --> 01:11:30,359
What'd I do?!

1069
01:11:42,572 --> 01:11:43,630
Don't fight anymore.

1070
01:11:43,740 --> 01:11:46,538
It's a free country,
don't fight anymore.

1071
01:11:47,911 --> 01:11:51,711
Aw, what'd I do?
What'd I do?

1072
01:11:56,086 --> 01:11:58,247
What'd I do?

1073
01:12:05,261 --> 01:12:07,229
- Get outta here!
- Jake has an interview--

1074
01:12:09,265 --> 01:12:12,234
It's all right, Jake.
It's all right.

1075
01:12:14,270 --> 01:12:16,738
Why did I do it? Why?

1076
01:12:22,345 --> 01:12:24,643
They got some balls,
some balls.

1077
01:12:25,882 --> 01:12:28,009
I take the dive.
What more do they want?

1078
01:12:28,551 --> 01:12:30,109
They want me
to go down, too?

1079
01:12:30,220 --> 01:12:32,688
I ain't goin' down.
I ain't goin' down for nobody.

1080
01:12:32,789 --> 01:12:35,417
Why don't you do me a favor?
Just put your hands up.

1081
01:12:35,525 --> 01:12:37,823
I wanna show you somethin'.
Put your hands up.

1082
01:12:39,062 --> 01:12:42,862
- What the fuck is so hard about that?
- Hey, you don't understand.

1083
01:12:43,967 --> 01:12:46,527
I had to fight a bum.
He's a bum.

1084
01:12:46,636 --> 01:12:49,537
I fought the guy, I tapped him like that,
all of a sudden he's like this

1085
01:12:49,639 --> 01:12:51,266
all over the place,
what am I gonna do?

1086
01:12:51,374 --> 01:12:53,467
You don't have to fuckin'
pick him up and help him.

1087
01:12:53,576 --> 01:12:55,271
What am I gonna do?
If I don't pick him up,

1088
01:12:55,378 --> 01:12:57,608
then what am I gonna do?
I'm gonna be in worse trouble.

1089
01:12:58,415 --> 01:12:59,939
I don't know.

1090
01:13:00,050 --> 01:13:03,076
"Purse was withheld--" look at this--
"Purse was withheld pending

1091
01:13:03,186 --> 01:13:05,245
D.A.'s probe."
Look at that.

1092
01:13:05,355 --> 01:13:07,949
Look how they make me look.

1093
01:13:08,058 --> 01:13:10,083
Like a bum,
like a mammalucco.

1094
01:13:10,760 --> 01:13:11,727
A what?

1095
01:13:11,828 --> 01:13:14,092
Like the mammalucco of the year.

1096
01:13:14,197 --> 01:13:15,824
Tommy ain't gonna forget us.

1097
01:13:16,666 --> 01:13:19,226
You're gonna get your shot,
as long as he don't die.

1098
01:13:20,437 --> 01:13:22,428
- As long as who don't die?
- Tommy.

1099
01:13:22,539 --> 01:13:24,097
What are you talkin' about?

1100
01:13:24,207 --> 01:13:26,107
In other words,
Tommy ain't gonna forget ya,

1101
01:13:26,209 --> 01:13:27,437
you're gonna get your shot
if he don't die.

1102
01:13:27,544 --> 01:13:29,603
- Gotta make sure the guy stays alive.
- He got a disease or somethin'?

1103
01:13:29,713 --> 01:13:31,613
No, I'm just sayin',
I'm kiddin', like.

1104
01:13:31,715 --> 01:13:33,478
What's wrong with him?
Is somethin' wrong with him?

1105
01:13:33,583 --> 01:13:35,517
There ain't nothin' wrong with him,
that's the only way you wouldn't get it

1106
01:13:35,618 --> 01:13:38,519
- is if he dies, he won't be able to--
- What are you talkin' like that for?

1107
01:13:47,297 --> 01:13:48,787
What do you want me to do?
It's an outdoor arena.

1108
01:13:48,898 --> 01:13:51,696
What do you wanna do,
fight in the rain? It's a stadium.

1109
01:13:51,801 --> 01:13:53,393
You waited this long,
you can wait longer.

1110
01:13:54,070 --> 01:13:56,538
You wanna wait 24 hours?
I don't wanna wait no 24 hours.

1111
01:13:56,639 --> 01:13:59,699
I don't either, but we gotta,
so we'll wait. Hello?

1112
01:14:00,410 --> 01:14:03,470
- You guys wanna stop now?
- Get off the phone with them.

1113
01:14:03,580 --> 01:14:05,138
Why do you give them
the satisfaction?

1114
01:14:05,248 --> 01:14:07,546
- Get off the phone with them!
- He don't wanna talk to nobody.

1115
01:14:07,650 --> 01:14:09,811
How many times do we have
to tell ya? You hear him yellin'?

1116
01:14:09,919 --> 01:14:12,479
There's enough confusion up here.
Please, don't call.

1117
01:14:12,589 --> 01:14:15,888
No comment. Right.
Thank you. Bye!

1118
01:14:15,992 --> 01:14:17,983
Pains in the asses,
I don't believe them.

1119
01:14:18,094 --> 01:14:20,722
Why do you give them the satisfaction?
Why don't you just hang up on 'em?

1120
01:14:20,830 --> 01:14:22,730
- That's all.
- I'm gonna get somethin' to eat.

1121
01:14:22,832 --> 01:14:24,959
- What do you want to eat?
- I don't want nothin'.

1122
01:14:25,502 --> 01:14:26,628
I don't want nothin'.

1123
01:14:26,736 --> 01:14:28,704
Eat somethin',
you gotta eat somethin'.

1124
01:14:30,874 --> 01:14:33,342
You can't go without eatin'.
Eat a steak.

1125
01:14:33,443 --> 01:14:36,344
You chew it, you spit it out,
you'll still make the weight tomorrow.

1126
01:14:37,046 --> 01:14:38,479
You're worried about that?

1127
01:14:40,717 --> 01:14:43,015
I'll order a steak.
At least if you want it, it's here.

1128
01:14:43,119 --> 01:14:45,019
You don't want it,
do whatever you want with it.

1129
01:14:45,121 --> 01:14:47,555
- Go ahead.
- Vickie, what do you want?

1130
01:14:48,291 --> 01:14:50,122
Order me a piece of cake.

1131
01:14:50,226 --> 01:14:52,126
That's all you want
is a piece of cake?

1132
01:14:52,228 --> 01:14:55,857
Why don't you get a cheeseburger,
French fries? It's better for you.

1133
01:14:55,965 --> 01:14:57,956
- It's like a whole meal.
- Yeah, that's good.

1134
01:14:58,067 --> 01:14:59,534
That's good,
order me one of those.

1135
01:14:59,636 --> 01:15:01,570
Wait a minute,
what do you want to eat?

1136
01:15:01,671 --> 01:15:03,901
Since when did you
order one of those?

1137
01:15:04,674 --> 01:15:06,403
- That's what I want.
- It's a free country.

1138
01:15:06,509 --> 01:15:08,636
You order what you want.
Don't let nobody influence you.

1139
01:15:08,745 --> 01:15:10,872
I'm not tellin' her what to eat,
I was just suggesting.

1140
01:15:10,980 --> 01:15:12,914
What are you tellin' her
what to ask for?

1141
01:15:13,016 --> 01:15:16,144
I'm not tellin' her-- personally,
I don't give a fuck what she eats.

1142
01:15:16,252 --> 01:15:18,880
What were you tellin' her that for?

1143
01:15:18,988 --> 01:15:20,888
Order me a cheeseburger.

1144
01:15:23,860 --> 01:15:26,454
Just order her
a cheeseburger, that's all.

1145
01:15:27,664 --> 01:15:28,892
What the f--?

1146
01:15:28,998 --> 01:15:32,092
What are you guys doin' so long?
How long does this thing take to do?

1147
01:15:32,202 --> 01:15:33,169
Forty seconds.

1148
01:15:33,269 --> 01:15:35,829
Forty seconds is no good.
You gotta do it in 30 seconds.

1149
01:15:35,939 --> 01:15:38,066
